"},{"pid":"7090eb3c247a7a0cb04f9c3782810f4db5473cc4","tid":678240,"uid":30615,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-26T07:07:39.000Z","msg":"xun<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/150657_c7b33d06dc30d848e57e0254cedaec02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F150657_c7b33d06dc30d848e57e0254cedaec02.png&h=fe12238d&s={SIZE}\" />日<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/150700_75e58735fbc8531fe3d4c88b1c5cfc1c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F150700_75e58735fbc8531fe3d4c88b1c5cfc1c.png&h=353b0e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日行大潭水塘，有d 部分乾到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c523cf358332bae141bb948aa43ad69ba4f912e5","tid":678240,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T18:20:40.000Z","msg":"如果出現旱災制水,一定死人,問題死多少.<br />\n到時的天氣高溫會熱死老人家和弱者,加上無水清潔會引起衛生問題.<br />\n有人因為搶水打架和坐地起價(看看澳門出現100蚊一支水......)<br />\n香港要用水的行業一定停擺........還有什麼問題會出現?<br />\n<br />\nPS:我唔信廣東會加水給香港,因為他是香港的水源,香港旱災是上面大旱,或者是他關水喉.<br />\n<br />\n【天鴿襲澳門】停電期間狼胎加價 150元兩支水100元一盒叉燒飯<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/992714/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F992714%2F&d=FvKVFpRkfxLCbEuMlWiRZcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=83048979\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F992714%2F&h=e55b8132\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/992714/</a><br />\n<br />\n「天鴿」吹襲澳門期間造成嚴重破壞，不少地區更停電斷水。有當地藥房和餐廳座地起價，一支在香港賣10元有找的700毫升蒸餾水，昨日在澳門藥房竟賣兩支合共150元，有燒味店一盒叉燒飯賣100元。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛批評商店「發災難財」，「飯都算，兩支水真係離X曬譜」、「75蚊一支水，仲貴過酒店」。<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170824/_2017082410180266970.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: